DeÄiÅkenlik katsayÄ±sÄ± (Coefficient of variation)

# Create the function.
getdk <- function(d) {
   k <- 100*(sd(d)/mean(d))
}
d_1 <- c(degisken_1)
dk_1 <- getdk(d_1)
print(dk_1)
## [1] 3.932862
d_2 <- c(degisken_2)
dk_2 <- getdk(d_2)
print(dk_2)
## [1] 4.751852
